biolockj.node

Class ParsedSample

  • java.lang.Object
    • biolockj.node.ParsedSample
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ParsedSample>

    public class ParsedSample
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<ParsedSample>
    ParserModules create and store one ParsedSample, with OTU assignments and counts, for each sample. Only the samples that contain one or more reads used by ClassifierModule to generate a valid taxonomic assignment are used.
    See Also:
